I'm just gonna enjoy the moments and cherish it forever.. 🥺 I just love my life.. like I said don't rush it if not your body will make yourself slow down. Listen to it and rest every once in a while... That's all for my log for this time.. till next time! Stay Strong! https://t.co/aX9uLBW7MF

I think our lives will be better.. I know. It's been like four months since I became this happy. Idky but I felt happy for once in my life in terms of friendship.. Yeah you can have a lot of down sides but good things are gonna happen. Good things are happening..

I never felt so grateful in my life. I know this friendship MEANS something and Allah told everyone to have a break. After that break once you're feeling a little better. You come back a new view in life. Life isn't easy but if you see the bigger picture..

That moment when I faced her.. that moment felt so good. Felt home. Felt like I have missed this feeling and it's been locked away since problem after problems.. I felt so good that my world gotten a little brighter. I knew I forgave her.. I know I forgave the situation...

Well after that things got alot better. In terms of my mental state but alot better. Idk how I just felt a little happier with life.. I am still tired but not as down as I use to be . I felt alot better maybe because my previous friend who I thought I wasn't ready to face..

Which sometimes makes me sad but I know I am making progress of it! That enough said. Well February was at the point where I took alot of leaves to get myself catch up with my pace.. me working in a fast pace area made me want to slow down again. I needed to slow down.

Well it's a start.. I know I will be old when I get marriage but I came to also realised that there isn't any rush for my relationship.. I already feel that we are already married at heart and it just isn't legal yet..
